CSC 407 Project
Ethan Engert and Ezra Nagel

To run:
    python -m venv .venv
    source .venv/bin/activate
    pip install -r requirements.txt

Create mysql database if not done already:
    mysql -u root -p
    
    CREATE DATABASE yellowbox_db;
    CREATE USER 'yellowbox_user'@'localhost' IDENTIFIED BY 'password';
    GRANT ALL PRIVILEGES ON yellowbox_db.* TO 'yellowbox_user'@'localhost';
    FLUSH PRIVILEGES;

Create Tables and Run:
    cd yellowbox
    python app.py
    exit running app
    python createTables.py
    python app.py

If messed up:
    python clearTables.py

    
    
